    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is strong, the transmission shifts smoothly, and it offers a comfortable, reliable driving experience for any commute. While it shows some minor signs of normal wear typical for its age, the interior is clean and all major systems are fully functional. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a quality pre-owned vehicle that is ready for the road.",
